They hide their scabby scalps under glamourous wigs and bury their menacing claws inside elegant gloves, but don’t let their dazzling purple eyes and sparkling accessories blind you to the truth. They are evil. They are vicious. And, yeah, OK, they’re a little bit fabulous. If Halloween has your inner witch itching to break free, wipe away that human veneer and reveal your devilish grin to show us just how much you are #ThatWitch! Then make sure to stream #TheWitches movie on HBOMax October 22.
